'''Gwayne Corbray''' is an unseen character in ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]''. He is long dead before the start of the series, and thus is not expected to appear. Ser Gwayne Corbray was a renowned [[Knighthood|knight]] of [[House Corbray]] and member of the [[Kingsguard]] under King [[Daeron II Targaryen]].

